        <updateDate>2019-04-19T21:54:19Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Commodity Futures Trading Commission Research and Development Modernization Act </b></p> <p>This bill modifies&nbsp;the requirement for&nbsp;the Commodity Futures Trading Commission to establish programs and perform research related to financial technologies, including to allow the commission to accept gifts and donations for&nbsp;such purposes. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
